    • getEntityTypeAndSubtypeNamesFromKey

      public TellrawUtils.Component[] getEntityTypeAndSubtypeNamesFromKey(String textureKey)
      Returns a localized Component[] where the first element is the entity's type and subsequent elements describe the sub-types. The ordering of sub-types is the same as their corresponding names in textureKey.split("|").
      Parameters:
      textureKey - a texture key describing the entity
      Returns:
      localized components for type name and sub-type names
